OL,3,CMan charged with attempted rape and
OL,4,CGBH of pensioner in park
OL,6,FA 25-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fafter a woman in her 70s was the
OL,8,Fvictim of a sex attack in a park in
OL,9,FSheffield.
OL,11,FThe woman was in Concord Park in the
OL,12,FShiregreen area when she was assaulted
OL,13,Fshortly before 7.30am on Wednesday, 25
OL,14,FMarch.
OL,16,FAli Askre, of no fixed address, has
OL,17,Fbeen charged with attempted rape and
OL,18,Fcausing grievous bodily harm with
OL,19,Fintent.
