OL,3,CMan charged with attempted rape and
OL,4,CGBH of pensioner in park
OL,6,FHe was due to appear at Sheffield
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the
OL,10,Fvictim, who was taken to hospital with
OL,11,Fserious injuries, is recovering well.
